  "description": "Thunder Software Technology Co.,Ltd. provides operating systems and on-device AI products and technologies in China, Europe, the United States, Japan, and internationally. The company offers pre and post silicon products; Smart Robotics Solutions, such as high, medium, and low computing power system on module and robot brain solutions; Edge AI station, IoT harbor, AIoT turnkey platform products; and Kanzi-3D engine and HMI toolchain. It also provides vehicle OS and HPC products; smart cockpit platforms, smart drive and vision, automatic test product toolchain; IoT OS products; IoT computing platform; and smart devices, including XR, handy terminals, video conference and live streaming, and arm server, as well as smart wearables, cameras, and speakers. In addition, the company offers system software solutions and customization comprising smartphone solutions and carrier certification services. Thunder Software Technology Co.,Ltd. was founded in 2008 and is headquartered in Beijing, China.",
